From f0b3e75d43ee2518aa3f044f4cbb1230340cca10 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 20:53:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Add product images/type/brand, multi-filter search,
 WhatsApp share, and perf/UI overhaul

- Schema: add images (JSON array), type (default unassigned), brand (default generic) to items table with migration
- Form: multi-image upload with client-side compression/resize before storage
- New ProductCard grid view with WhatsApp share button per product
- Search view: multi-parameter filtering (type, brand, stock status, text)
- Route-level code splitting and manual vendor chunking for faster loads
- Minimal high-contrast theme refresh
