From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 20:53:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Migrate persistence to Supabase, USD-canonical pricing,
 RPC-based user management

Replace sql.js/localforage with Supabase (Postgres + Storage). Prices are
now stored canonically in USD with BS/EUR conversion at display time.
Admins manage sellers via SECURITY DEFINER RPCs. WhatsApp share now
includes the carousel image, USD price, display price, and brand.
